experiment DCSscint
instrument HEA
start 2015 02 05 1400
end 2015 02 05 1600
status R
description Investigation of heater-stimulated ionospheric scintillations
contact Olesia Charkina
email charkina@rian.kharkov.ua
operator Michael Rietveld
submitter Olesia Charkina
resources UA(8)
notes
Investigation of scintillation intensity for discreet cosmic source (DCS) 
radiation in the modified polar ionosphere. Analyzing the characteristic features 
of DCS scintillations induced by natural and artificial inhomogeneities of a 
Fresnel size in the ionospheric F-layer.
